(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
(7. IMPLICATIONS FOR HUMAN-AI COLLABORATION) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(Lessons from this case study:) show newline
() show newline
(  * Context persistence matters - collaboration without memory is hobbled) show newline
(  * Vocabulary emergence is natural - don't force terminology, let it arise from use) show newline
(  * The human provides taste - knowing what to keep, what to discard, what feels right) show newline
(  * The AI provides throughput - implementing, exploring, handling mechanical transformation) show newline
(  * Neither dominates - this is partnership, not tool use) show newline
() show newline
(The methodology scales. Any sufficiently complex domain could benefit) show newline
(from this approach: accumulated context, shared vocabulary, delta) show newline
(communication, iterative refinement.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
